<section class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h1 class="fw-bold text-uppercase text-danger">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-muted fst-italic">Effective Date: August 1, 2025</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-dark" style="line-height: 1.7;">
        <p>
            At <strong>SK LADIES CORNER</strong>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you visit or make a purchase from our website.
